Package: com.github.amkay.gradle.gitflow.version

[Groovy] Class DelayedVersionWithType

    • com.github.amkay.gradle.gitflow.version.DelayedVersionWithType
    • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
      Comparable

      class DelayedVersionWithType
extends Object

      A helper class with the API of com.github.zafarkhaja.semver.Version that uses the available strategies to infer the current version lazily. This class delegates to VersionWithType.
